body:
Hey so I've joined avicus a while back and only played a few tournaments, didn't really get into it until the last one. I'm not very known on this server so I wanted to maybe do an AMA for the people that cares! I'm from OCN/Badlion, I mostly play competitive stuff. My position on teams I play for is usually frontlines/shotcaller. I'm from Canada and my first language is french!

You can ask me anything and I will hopefully be able to answer it honestly.  

Thank you!

replies.body:
Hmm this is a hard one.

I think you take things very personally and can be clingy at times. You care a lot about what other people say about you and what they think of you. You are a very nice person with a lot of qualities and it's a shame that people affect you that much. Sometimes your personality seems to be copying someone else's, kinda like lordblox in a sense. You should stick with your own personality because it's a good one :) .

I mean I've been in a lot of "high pressure" environment in regards of this game and this one really wasn't one of them. I knew we had the superior shot-calling + we could compete in all the other areas so I wasn't that worried.
